sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as User
  participant Page as SharePoint Classic Page
  participant Loader as chat-loader.js
  participant SP as _spPageContextInfo.aadTokenProviderFactory
  participant BFF as BFF (/chat/session)
  participant AES as Agent Execution Service
  participant MCP as MCP Protected API

  User->>Page: Open classic page
  Page->>Loader: Load script
  Loader->>SP: getTokenProvider().getToken(bffResourceUri)
  SP-->>Loader: Delegated bearer token
  Note over Loader: In-memory only; no localStorage/sessionStorage token writes
  Loader->>Loader: Generate traceparent
  Loader->>BFF: POST /chat/session<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>traceparent + {display_name?}
  Note over Loader,BFF: userId/display_name is display-only context, never identity
  BFF->>BFF: Validate bearer token (identity source)
  BFF->>AES: Forward request + traceparent
  AES->>MCP: OBO call + traceparent
  MCP-->>AES: Response
  AES-->>BFF: Session payload
  BFF-->>Loader: {session_id, expires_at}
  Loader-->>Page: Render session status
